00:27:29,017 --> 00:27:30,317
And the more people got involved,

560
00:27:30,317 --> 00:27:32,139
the more they were actually giving us feedback

561
00:27:32,139 --> 00:27:34,600
and giving us great ideas that we probably never

562
00:27:34,600 --> 00:27:35,421
would have come up with.

563
00:27:35,421 --> 00:27:37,642
Yeah, and one thing also is that, real quick,

